text:
Hi! I'm trying to create a module for an email that lets the text and button on the right align with the image on the left. Currently its leaving some spacing issues. Im also trying to see if its able to be mobile friendly. I'm super savvy when it comes to coding for these so I was wondering if anyone can help identify what's the issue with this module.

{% set image = module.image %}
{% set small_text = module.small_text %}
{% set headline = module.headline %}
{% set text = module.body_text %}
{% set button_text = module.button_text %}
{% set button_url = module.button_url.href %}

&lt;div style="display: flex; align-items: stretch; gap: 20px;"&gt;
  &lt;!-- Left Image --&gt;
  &lt;div style="flex: 1.5; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center;"&gt;
    &lt;img src="{{ module.image_field.src }}" alt="Image" style="width: 100%; max-width: 400px; height: auto; border-radius: 8px;"&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;

  &lt;!-- Right Content --&gt;
  &lt;div style="flex: 2; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: space-between; text-align: left; position: relative;"&gt;
    &lt;!-- Ornament and Small Text --&gt;
    &lt;div style="display: flex; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 10px;"&gt;
      &lt;!-- Ornament Image --&gt;
      &lt;img src="<https://www.google.com/url?sa=i&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.citypng.com%2Fsearch%3Fq%3Dornament%2Bball%2Btransparent&amp;psig=AOvVaw2ORkfgVLfHVb_p7tbCfzr1&amp;ust=1732808982792000&amp;source=images&amp;cd=vfe&amp;opi=89978449&amp;ved=0CBQQjRxqFwoTCNDamd3u_IkDFQAAAAAdAAAAABAE>" alt="Ornament" style="width: 30px; height: auto; margin-right: 10px;"&gt;

      &lt;!-- Small Text --&gt;
      &lt;span style="font-size: 14px; color: #777; line-height: 1.2;"&gt;{{ small_text }}&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;

    &lt;!-- Main Headline --&gt;
    &lt;h2 style="font-size: 24px; margin-top: 5px;"&gt;{{ headline }}&lt;/h2&gt;

    &lt;!-- Main Content Text --&gt;
    &lt;p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 20px;"&gt;{{ text }}&lt;/p&gt;

    &lt;!-- Button --&gt;
    &lt;div&gt;
      &lt;a href="{{ button_url }}"
        style="padding: 10px 20px;
           background-color: #D4B47A;
           color: #fff;
           text-decoration: none;
           font-size: 16px;
           border-radius: 20px;
           display: inline-block;"&gt;
        {{ button_text }}
      &lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
